label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"鸡马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":8,"end":13,"text":"疱疹病毒群","labels":["disease"]},{"start":14,"end":21,"text":"B亚群疱疹病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":24,"end":31,"text":"鸡肿瘤性传染病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 鸡马立克氏病是由疱疹病毒群的B亚群疱疹病毒引起的鸡肿瘤性传染病。

label: [{"start":1,"end":2,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"外周神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":8,"end":10,"text":"性腺","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":15,"text":"内脏器官","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":16,"end":18,"text":"虹膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"肌肉","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"皮肤","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":29,"end":34,"text":"淋巴性肿瘤","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 以鸡的外周神经、性腺、内脏器官、虹膜、肌肉和皮肤等组织形成淋巴性肿瘤为特征。

label: [{"start":0,"end":1,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":33,"end":34,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":3,"end":9,"text":"鸡马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":10,"end":14,"text":"死亡率高","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":15,"end":20,"text":"产蛋率下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":21,"end":25,"text":"免疫抑制","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":26,"end":31,"text":"进行性衰弱","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 鸡感染鸡马立克氏病后死亡率高，产蛋率下降，免疫抑制及进行性衰弱，是鸡的重要传染病之一。

label: [{"start":10,"end":11,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":20,"end":21,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: (一)流行病学特征、鸡最易感，各种日龄的鸡均可感染，但自然感染最早发生于3~4周龄，一般多发于2～5月龄。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"带毒鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":7,"end":13,"text":"鸡马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":24,"end":27,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 病鸡和带毒鸡是鸡马立克氏病重要的传染来源，主要经呼吸道传染。

label: [{"start":7,"end":14,"text":"免疫抑制性疾病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":18,"end":24,"text":"鸡马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 各种应激因素和免疫抑制性疾病均可促使鸡马立克氏病的发生。

label: [{"start":2,"end":11,"text":"神经型病鸡运动障碍","labels":["disease"]},{"start":12,"end":19,"text":"坐骨神经受侵害","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":12,"end":16,"text":"坐骨神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"劈叉姿势","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 1.神经型病鸡运动障碍，坐骨神经受侵害时表现劈叉姿势；

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"前臂神经受侵害","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"下垂","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":12,"end":13,"text":"翅","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"前臂神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":15,"text":"翅下垂","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 前臂神经受侵害时，则该侧翅下垂。

label: [{"start":0,"end":9,"text":"受侵害神经失去光泽","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":5,"end":9,"text":"失去光泽","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":11,"end":14,"text":"淡黄色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":15,"end":19,"text":"肿胀变粗","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":20,"end":24,"text":"横纹消失","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"受侵害神经","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 受侵害神经失去光泽，呈淡黄色，肿胀变粗，横纹消失。

label: [{"start":2,"end":5,"text":"内脏型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":7,"end":11,"text":"精神沉郁","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":12,"end":16,"text":"食欲减退","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"苍白","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":27,"text":"有萎缩","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":30,"end":32,"text":"腹泻","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":33,"end":38,"text":"渐进性消瘦","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":41,"end":47,"text":"内脏器官肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":45,"end":47,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":89,"end":91,"text":"肿块","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":17,"end":18,"text":"冠","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"肉髯","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":41,"end":45,"text":"内脏器官","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":49,"end":51,"text":"肝脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":52,"end":54,"text":"脾脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":55,"end":57,"text":"肾脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":58,"end":60,"text":"卵巢","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":61,"end":63,"text":"睾丸","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":69,"end":70,"text":"肝","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":71,"end":73,"text":"脾脏","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":19,"end":23,"text":"肉髯苍白","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 2.内脏型病鸡精神沉郁，食欲减退，冠和肉髯苍白或有萎缩，有时腹泻，渐进性消瘦，多种内脏器官肿大，以肝脏、脾脏、肾脏、卵巢、睾丸等多见，尤以肝、脾脏明显，见有形态、色泽、大小各异的肿块。

label: [{"start":2,"end":8,"text":"眼型视力障碍","labels":["disease"]},{"start":9,"end":14,"text":"虹膜呈灰色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"灰色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":15,"end":21,"text":"瞳孔边缘不整","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":17,"end":21,"text":"边缘不整","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":23,"end":26,"text":"锯齿状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":29,"end":32,"text":"灰眼病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":33,"end":36,"text":"白眼病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"虹膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"瞳孔","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 3.眼型视力障碍，虹膜呈灰色，瞳孔边缘不整、呈锯齿状，俗称灰眼病或白眼病。

label: [{"start":2,"end":5,"text":"皮肤型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":20,"end":23,"text":"小结节","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":27,"text":"瘤状物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":7,"text":"腿","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":8,"end":9,"text":"颈","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"躯干","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":13,"end":18,"text":"背部的羽囊","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 4.皮肤型在腿、颈、躯干和背部的羽囊形成小结节或瘤状物。

label: [{"start":16,"end":22,"text":"磷酸盐缓冲液","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 4.琼脂凝胶平板用含8%氯化钠的磷酸盐缓冲液(0.01摩尔/升，pH7.4)配制1%琼脂糖溶液，水浴加温使之充分熔化后，加入培养皿，每皿约加20毫升，平置，在室温下凝固冷却后，将琼脂板放在预先绘好的7孔形图案上，用打孔器按图形准确位置打孔，中心孔的孔径为4毫米，周边孔的孔径为3毫米，孔距约3毫米。

label: [{"start":17,"end":20,"text":"被检鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: (二)操作方法、1.检测血清抗体(被检鸡血清)

label: [{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"羽髓","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":17,"text":"被检鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 2.用阳性血清检测病毒抗原(被检鸡的羽髓浸液)

label: [{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"羽髓","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"翅羽","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"大羽","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":43,"end":45,"text":"羽根","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"幼鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"成鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: (1)选拔含羽髓丰满的翅羽或身体其他部位的大羽数根(幼鸡8根，中、成鸡3～5根),剪下羽根部分，并按编号分别收集于相应的小试管中。

label: [{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"羽髓","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"羽根","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":66,"end":68,"text":"羽髓","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (2)向每试管内滴加2～3滴蒸馏水(羽髓丰满时也可不加),然后用玻璃棒挤压羽根，以适当的压力转动玻璃棒，倾斜试管，并用玻璃棒导流，使羽髓浸液流至管口，另一人用加样品的吸管将其吸出，加入外周孔2中。

label: [{"start":2,"end":8,"text":"加强环境管理","labels":["control"]},{"start":8,"end":18,"text":"加强鸡场环境卫生管理","labels":["control"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"消毒","labels":["control"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"雏鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 1.加强环境管理加强鸡场环境卫生管理与消毒工作，防止雏鸡早期感染。

label: [{"start":2,"end":8,"text":"加强饲养管理","labels":["control"]},{"start":8,"end":14,"text":"加强饲养管理","labels":["control"]}]
text: 2.加强饲养管理加强饲养管理，提高机体抗病能力。

label: [{"start":5,"end":9,"text":"全进全出","labels":["control"]},{"start":15,"end":19,"text":"全进全出","labels":["control"]},{"start":28,"end":29,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 3.实行“全进全出”制度实行“全进全出”,防止不同日龄的鸡混养。

label: [{"start":23,"end":27,"text":"免疫抑制","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":2,"end":8,"text":"防止应激刺激","labels":["control"]},{"start":8,"end":17,"text":"防止应激因素的刺激","labels":["control"]}]
text: 4,防止应激刺激防止应激因素的刺激和预防能引起免疫抑制的疾病。

label: [{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"免疫接种","labels":["control"]},{"start":9,"end":15,"text":"鸡马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":33,"end":41,"text":"火鸡疱疹病毒疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":42,"end":46,"text":"HVT苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":66,"end":74,"text":"CV1988疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":75,"end":80,"text":"814疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":50,"end":54,"text":"3型疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":55,"end":59,"text":"2型疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":60,"end":64,"text":"1型疫苗","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 5.免疫接种是控制鸡马立克氏病的基本措施目前使用的疫苗有很多种，如火鸡疱疹病毒疫苗(HVT苗),或称3型疫苗、2型疫苗、1型疫苗(如CV1988疫苗、814疫苗)等；

label: [{"start":1,"end":4,"text":"进口苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":5,"end":8,"text":"国产苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":39,"end":41,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":45,"end":50,"text":"1日龄雏鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 有进口苗和国产苗。但它们的保护率均达不到100%,究其原因，可能是多方面的，如疫苗的质量、1日龄雏鸡的免疫技术、生长发育阶段的环境条件等。

label: [{"start":6,"end":12,"text":"鸡马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 所以为了防制鸡马立克氏病，减少经济损失，采取综合性防制措施非常必要。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"鸡马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"疱疹病毒","labels":["disease"]},{"start":25,"end":33,"text":"高度接触性传染病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":17,"end":24,"text":"淋巴细胞增生性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":24,"text":"增生性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":17,"end":21,"text":"淋巴细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 鸡马立克氏病是由疱疹病毒引起的一种淋巴细胞增生性、高度接触性传染病。

label: [{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":30,"end":36,"text":"淋巴细胞浸润","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":34,"end":36,"text":"浸润","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":42,"end":44,"text":"肿瘤","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":6,"end":10,"text":"外周神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"性腺","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":16,"text":"虹膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"脏器","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"肌肉","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"皮肤","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":30,"end":34,"text":"淋巴细胞","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 特点是病鸡的外周神经、性腺、虹膜、各种脏器、肌肉和皮肤等发生淋巴细胞浸润、肿大，形成肿瘤。

label: [{"start":0,"end":1,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"雌鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":27,"end":29,"text":"雄鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 鸡年龄越小越易感，通常多出现在2~5月龄的鸡群；雌鸡比雄鸡易感。

label: [{"start":5,"end":6,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":7,"end":13,"text":"鸡马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":34,"end":36,"text":"肉鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":41,"end":43,"text":"蛋鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":44,"end":47,"text":"来航鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":52,"end":55,"text":"本地鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 不同品种的鸡对鸡马立克氏病的抵抗力及感染后发病率有一定差异，一般认为肉鸡易感性大于蛋鸡，来航鸡易感性大于本地鸡。

label: [{"start":14,"end":20,"text":"维生素A缺乏","labels":["disease"]},{"start":21,"end":24,"text":"鸡球虫","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 一些应激因素、饲养管理不良、维生素A缺乏、鸡球虫的存在等均可增加发病率。

label: [{"start":3,"end":8,"text":"鸡贫血因子","labels":["disease"]},{"start":27,"end":28,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":29,"end":35,"text":"严重免疫抑制","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 此外，鸡贫血因子已引起国内外学者的极大关注，因其可造成鸡的严重免疫抑制。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"带毒鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":7,"end":13,"text":"鸡马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"鸡群","labels":["type"]}]
text: 病鸡和带毒鸡是鸡马立克氏病的传染源，鸡群不论直接或间接接触都能传播病毒。

label: [{"start":8,"end":10,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":38,"end":40,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":60,"end":61,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":11,"end":14,"text":"分泌物","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":18,"text":"排泄物","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"皮肤","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":24,"end":28,"text":"羽囊上皮","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":47,"end":50,"text":"羽毛屑","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 病毒可通过空气和病鸡的分泌物、排泄物传播，皮肤的羽囊上皮是含病毒最多的部位，病鸡身上脱落下来的羽毛屑含有很多病毒，一旦被鸡吸入或食入都能感染发病。

label: [{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"吸血昆虫","labels":["disease"]},{"start":10,"end":16,"text":"鸡马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 此外吸血昆虫也可能是鸡马立克氏病的传播媒介。

label: [{"start":16,"end":19,"text":"神经型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":20,"end":23,"text":"内脏型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"眼型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":27,"end":30,"text":"皮肤型","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 根据症状和病变发生的部位，可分为神经型、内脏型、眼型和皮肤型四类、有时可以混合发生。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"神经型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":25,"end":26,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":31,"end":33,"text":"神经","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (1)神经型。最常见的一型，主要发生在3~4月龄的鸡。因受损的神经不同表现的症状有所不同。

label: [{"start":1,"end":7,"text":"坐骨神经受损","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"受损","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":1,"end":5,"text":"坐骨神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":21,"text":"双腿发生麻痹","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":19,"end":21,"text":"麻痹","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":35,"end":42,"text":"特征性劈叉姿势","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":48,"end":52,"text":"卧地不起","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":13,"end":14,"text":"腿","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"双腿","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":25,"end":27,"text":"一肢","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":30,"end":32,"text":"一肢","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":57,"end":59,"text":"厌食","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":60,"end":62,"text":"失水","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":63,"end":65,"text":"贫血","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":66,"end":68,"text":"昏迷","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":69,"end":73,"text":"体重减轻","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 当坐骨神经受损时，病鸡一条腿或双腿发生麻痹，表现为一肢向前另一肢向后的特征性劈叉姿势,也可表现为卧地不起；此外还有厌食、失水、贫血、昏迷和体重减轻等症状。

label: [{"start":1,"end":6,"text":"臂神经受害","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"受害","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":1,"end":4,"text":"臂神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":8,"end":10,"text":"病鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":13,"end":19,"text":"两侧翅膀下垂","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"下垂","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":20,"end":31,"text":"支配颈部肌肉的神经受损","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"受损","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":35,"end":37,"text":"扭头","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":38,"end":40,"text":"仰头","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":43,"end":51,"text":"颈部迷走神经受损","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":49,"end":51,"text":"受损","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":53,"end":57,"text":"嗦囊麻痹","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":55,"end":57,"text":"麻痹","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":58,"end":60,"text":"扩张","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":61,"end":63,"text":"失声","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":64,"end":68,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"翅膀","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":20,"end":29,"text":"支配颈部肌肉的神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":36,"end":37,"text":"头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":39,"end":40,"text":"头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":43,"end":49,"text":"颈部迷走神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":53,"end":55,"text":"嗦囊","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 当臂神经受害时，病鸡一侧或两侧翅膀下垂：支配颈部肌肉的神经受损时，引起扭头、仰头现象；颈部迷走神经受损时，嗦囊麻痹、扩张，失声，呼吸困难；

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"腹部神经受损","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"受损","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":18,"end":27,"text":"受损的神经失去光泽","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":23,"end":27,"text":"失去光泽","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":28,"end":32,"text":"颜色变暗","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":33,"end":35,"text":"淡黄","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":36,"end":40,"text":"横纹消失","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":41,"end":47,"text":"局部肿胀增粗","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":66,"end":70,"text":"一侧受损","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":4,"text":"腹部神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"腹泻","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":18,"end":23,"text":"受损的神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":61,"end":63,"text":"神经","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":76,"end":78,"text":"神经","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 腹部神经受损时，常表现腹泻：剖检可见受损的神经失去光泽，颜色变暗或淡黄，横纹消失，局部肿胀增粗，大于正常的2~3倍，对称的神经通常是一侧受损，易与正常的神经比较。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"内脏型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"幼鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":17,"end":21,"text":"精神委顿","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":22,"end":27,"text":"渐进性消痴","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":30,"end":34,"text":"衰竭死亡","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: (2)内脏型。多发于幼鸡，主要表现精神委顿，渐进性消痴|最终衰竭死亡。

label: [{"start":9,"end":13,"text":"突然死亡","labels":["symptom"]}]
text: 也有的不表现症状，突然死亡。发病率高，死亡率可达60%以上。

label: [{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"肿瘤结节","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":27,"text":"黄白色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"质硬","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":36,"end":39,"text":"油脂状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"脏器","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":18,"end":23,"text":"外观灰白色","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 剖检可见脏器上有大小不等的肿瘤结节，外观灰白色或黄白色，质硬，切面平整呈油脂状。

label: [{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"脏器","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"脏器","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"脏器","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":18,"text":"浸润于脏器内","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"浸润","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":20,"end":26,"text":"脏器异常增大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":26,"text":"异常增大","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 有的突出于脏器表面，有的浸润于脏器内，使脏器异常增大。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"鸡马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":17,"end":24,"text":"鸡淋巴性白血病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":8,"end":13,"text":"法氏囊萎缩","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"萎缩","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":8,"end":11,"text":"法氏囊","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 鸡马立克氏病多使法氏囊萎缩，这是与鸡淋巴性白血病的主要区别。

label: [{"start":3,"end":5,"text":"眼型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":6,"end":8,"text":"单眼","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":9,"end":11,"text":"双眼","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":14,"end":20,"text":"虹膜色素消失","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":18,"end":20,"text":"消失","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":24,"text":"灰色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":18,"text":"虹膜色素","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":28,"end":31,"text":"灰眼病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":34,"end":37,"text":"鸡白眼","labels":["disease"]}]
text: (3)眼型。单眼或双眼发病，虹膜色素消失，呈灰色，俗称“灰眼病”或“鸡白眼”；

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"瞳孔边缘不齐","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"边缘不齐","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":8,"end":11,"text":"锯齿状","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":12,"end":18,"text":"瞳孔逐渐缩小","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":14,"end":18,"text":"逐渐缩小","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":19,"end":23,"text":"视力减退","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"瞳孔","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":12,"end":14,"text":"瞳孔","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 瞳孔边缘不齐，呈锯齿状，瞳孔逐渐缩小，视力减退或消失。

label: [{"start":3,"end":6,"text":"皮肤型","labels":["disease"]},{"start":15,"end":17,"text":"肿瘤","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":40,"end":43,"text":"小结节","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":44,"end":47,"text":"瘤状物","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":48,"end":51,"text":"病程长","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":21,"end":23,"text":"翅膀","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":24,"end":25,"text":"颈","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":26,"end":27,"text":"背","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":28,"end":30,"text":"大腿","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":32,"end":34,"text":"皮肤","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":36,"end":38,"text":"毛囊","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: (4)皮肤型。一般无临床症状，肿瘤多发生于翅膀、颈、背、大腿等处皮肤，使毛囊形成小结节或瘤状物，病程长。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"鸡马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":22,"end":28,"text":"做好预防工作","labels":["control"]}]
text: 鸡马立克氏病目前尚无有效的治疗方法，重要的是做好预防工作。

label: [{"start":3,"end":10,"text":"搞好卫生与管理","labels":["control"]},{"start":14,"end":20,"text":"鸡马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":49,"end":55,"text":"鸡马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"幼鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":28,"end":32,"text":"免疫接种","labels":["control"]}]
text: (1)搞好卫生与管理。幼鸡对鸡马立克氏病易感性极高，即使免疫接种质量很好，如果在出壳前4周内接触到鸡马立克氏病的强毒，可能仍有发病的。

label: [{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"隔离进行","labels":["control"]},{"start":18,"end":29,"text":"搞好鸡舍的环境消毒工作","labels":["control"]},{"start":30,"end":36,"text":"定期进行驱虫","labels":["control"]},{"start":44,"end":47,"text":"球虫病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 因此1~90日龄育雏阶段应隔离进行。搞好鸡舍的环境消毒工作，定期进行驱虫，特别要注意预防球虫病。

label: [{"start":3,"end":8,"text":"马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":41,"end":47,"text":"鸡马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":26,"end":28,"text":"消毒","labels":["control"]},{"start":29,"end":36,"text":"种鸡要隔离饲养","labels":["control"]},{"start":12,"end":13,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":29,"end":31,"text":"种鸡","labels":["type"]}]
text: 不从有马立克氏病的鸡场进鸡、进种蛋，购买的种蛋要进行消毒，种鸡要隔离饲养，一旦发现鸡马立克氏病全部淘汰。

label: [{"start":3,"end":7,"text":"预防接种","labels":["control"]},{"start":10,"end":11,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":16,"end":22,"text":"尽早接种疫苗","labels":["control"]},{"start":23,"end":27,"text":"免疫接种","labels":["control"]}]
text: (2)预防接种。所有鸡均在出壳后尽早接种疫苗，免疫接种与接触强毒的时间间隔越长，免疫效果越好。

label: [{"start":17,"end":19,"text":"鸡胚","labels":["type"]},{"start":21,"end":25,"text":"免疫接种","labels":["control"]},{"start":27,"end":28,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":35,"end":41,"text":"鸡马立克氏病","labels":["disease"]}]
text: 近年来，国外有人对18~19日龄的鸡胚进行免疫接种，使鸡一出壳就具有对鸡马立克氏病的抵抗力，效果令人满意。

label: [{"start":0,"end":6,"text":"火鸡疱疹病毒","labels":["drug"]},{"start":27,"end":28,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":28,"end":35,"text":"皮下或肌内注射","labels":["control"]}]
text: 火鸡疱疹病毒(HVT)苗，使用时按瓶签说明稀释后，每只鸡皮下或肌内注射0.2mL。

label: [{"start":11,"end":13,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 疫苗现用现配，稀释好的疫苗应放入盛有冰块的容器中，必须在1小时内用完。

label: [{"start":0,"end":7,"text":"自然低毒力弱毒","labels":["drug"]},{"start":13,"end":15,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]}]
text: 自然低毒力弱毒(814株)疫苗：必须在液氮中保存及运输。

label: [{"start":2,"end":3,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":3,"end":10,"text":"肌肉或皮下注射","labels":["control"]}]
text: 每只鸡肌肉或皮下注射0.2mL,注苗后3天可产生免疫力，免疫持续期为一年半。
